headline.main: Russians Strike in Center; Germans Report a Victory; RED ARMY STRIKES AT FOE IN CENTER

lead_paragraph: MOSCOW, Tuesday, Sept. 30 -- Red Army troops counter-attacking in the central and southern sectors have succeeded in breaking up German tank concentrations southwest of Bryansk and routing two brigades of Rumanian infantry in the Ukraine, ...
abstract: USSR forces break up German tank units, Bryansk area, and rout 2 Rumanian infantry divs, Ukraine
